title: (Thurs Full) Major Update from our Favorite 6th Grader and Her Talent Show Request for Jason Aldean  + Throwback Thursday! + Morgan Needs Help with an Walk Up Music for Celeb Softball Game
itunes:title: (Thurs Full) Major Update from our Favorite 6th Grader and Her Talent Show Request for Jason Aldean  + Throwback Thursday! + Morgan Needs Help with an Walk Up Music for Celeb Softball Game
description:
We get an update from 6th Grader Reese who called in trying to get Jason Aldean to come perform at her talent show.  Bobby shares big events that all happened on this day in country music. It will talk you back in the best way. Morgan is playing in a celebrity softball and asks Bobby for help picking an entrance song.
